quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  20,52,"Avuga ati:- ubumenyi bwivyo vyose buri k’Umuremyi buri mugitabu cayo, Umuremyi wanje atazimira canke atibagira"
  20,53,"Ariyo yabagiriye iy’Isi kuba ubusaswa nukuba girira muriyo amayira hamwe nukuba manurira amazi avuye mubicu, no kuriyo twanagishijeko ubwoko bw’imbuto zitandukanye"
  20,54,"Nimufungure kandi murishe ibitungwa vyanyu, ntankeka muri ibi vyose harimwo ibimenyetso ku bantu bafise ubwenge"
  20,55,"Kuri iy’Isi niho twabaremeye, no muriyo niho tuzoba subizamwo, no kuva muriyo niho tuzoba kuramwo ubugira kabiri"
  20,56,"Mu vy’ukuri twaramweretse Fir’auni ibimenyetso vyacu vyose, mugabo yarabi hakanye aravyanka"
  20,57,"Avuga ati:- uje kudukura mugihugu cacu ukoresheje uburozi bwawe wewe Musa"
  20,58,"Rero twebwe tuzo kuzanira uburozi bumeze nkubwo bw’iwawe, rero nugire isango riri hagati yacu na wewe, atari ayo twebwe tuzosenyura canke wewe, hanyuma tuze duhurire ahantu hateguwe neza"
  20,59,"Intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii) ivuga iti:- isango ryanyu n’umusi mukuru w’ibisharizo n’abantu baze bakoranywe mugitondo"
  20,60,Fir’auni aragaruka nugutegura imigambi yiwe hanyuma arashika n’abarozi biwe
  20,61,"Intumwa y’Imana Musa (iii) ibabwira iti: mwa bantu mwe! ntimwadukane ububeshi hejuru y’Imana ntize ibahanagure kubera ibihano vyayo, nayo uwadukana ibintu ntantsinzi afise"
  20,62,"Rero barahaririye kuri urwo rubanza ruri hagati yabo, baca barupfundika mumwiherero"
  20,63,"Bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri aba bantu babiri n’abarozi bagomba babakura mugihugu canyu bakoresheje uburozi bwabo, kandi bagomba kubakurira imico n’imigenzo yanyu myiza mufise"
  20,64,"Kuri ivyo rero nimwegeranye ivyanyu vyose hanyuma muje iwabo mutonze kumirongo, mu vy’ukuri kuri uno musi uri hejuru hazotsinda uwuzotsinda"